import React from 'react'
import {Drawer, IconButton} from '@material-ui/core'
import CloseIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Close'





const Cart = () => {
    return (
        <Drawer
        anchor="left"
        >
            <IconButton>
            <CloseIcon/>
            </IconButton>
        </Drawer>
    )
}

export default Cart
